---
title: Plant-Based Protein Tex-Mex Messy Janes with Pickled Onion, Roasted Potato Wedges & Lime Mayo
description: Craving the ultimate throwback of the humble sloppy joe—minus the meat? Look no further. This version stars Tex-Mex–spiced plant-based protein, and is worlds tastier than the ones the lunch lady slung: Think pickled onion, a savory sauce, and a side of hearty potato wedges. (We’d still highly recommend keeping a few napkins nearby, though.)
